definitions.definition: A common East Asian liquid sauce , made by subjecting boiled beans to long fermentation and then long digestion in salt and water .
examples: I like a little soy with my rice.

definitions.definition: ( uncountable , often attributive ) Soybeans , or the protein derived from them.
examples: These candles are made from soy .
The soy crop is looking good this year.
This diet doesn't let me eat soy .
